code: @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") @Override protected TypeComparator<Time> createComparator(boolean ascending) {     return (TypeComparator) new DateComparator(ascending). }
@Override protected TypeSerializer<Time> createSerializer() {     return new SqlTimeSerializer(). }
@Override protected Time[] getSortedTestData() {     return new Time[] { Time.valueOf("00:00:00"), Time.valueOf("02:42:25"), Time.valueOf("14:15:59"), Time.valueOf("18:00:45") }. }
